#### Link for ansible vault documentation
  * https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/user_guide/vault.html#ansible-vault
 
#### Command line options with (ansible-vault)
  * create
    * to create ansible vault in encrypted format
  * view
    * to view data of encrypted file
  * edit 
    * to edit the encrypted file
  * encrypt
    * to encrypt an unencrypted file
  * decrypt
    * to decrypt an encrypted file
  * --ask-vault-pass
    * to provide password while running playbook
  * --vault-password-file
    * to pass a vault password through a file
